    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Your article might have mentioned the power women are exercising in the marketplace by buying ''green'' products. In the long run, of course, we need regulation and legislation. In the short term, intervention by those who rule the marketplace -- women -- may provide the tipping point.</p>
      </block>
